<br>Hi,<br><br>I downloaded the nightly trunk snapshot openmpi-1.7a1r23032. I recompiled openmpi and my test code, and put back the btl_tcp_eager_limit to default.<br>The bug seems to be fixed. I don&#39;t have the segfault anymore even with big array (up to 685MB).  <br>

Thanks to all the developpers. <br><br>There is a ticket on the bug trac about this problem that may need to be updated :<br><a href="https://svn.open-mpi.org/trac/ompi/ticket/2336">https://svn.open-mpi.org/trac/ompi/ticket/2336</a><br>

